snippet.title: Chex Quest HD Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Chex Quest HD will be a 5-level, single player first person shooter, suitable for all ages just like the original cereal box prize from 1996. This will be a free game! No upfront cost, no in-game purchases... just free to anyone who wants to play it!

You can follow the development of the game at facebook.com/ChexQuestHD

Chex (TM) is a registered trademark of General Mills, Inc. and permission for its use has been given for this remake.
